creator: messer_amd
descriptionHtml:
This is a simple free application that helps you and makes the process of going to the store easier and more efficient.
You can easily create your shopping lists and share them with your friends.
All data is stored on app library, so you will always have access to it.
By making only pre-planned purchases, you can avoid the tricks of marketers and save your money.
The application does not collect or share your personal data.
In addition, you can create your own personal notes, which will also be useful for you.
I will be grateful for your suggestions, feedback and ratings.
Thank you!
